-- New York Marathon Runners to Have Baggage Options at Race
-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 2012-09-06T18:35:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-06/new-york-marathon-runners-to-have-baggage-options-at-race.html
New York  Marathon runners will have
the option of taking a no baggage “early exit,” or checking a
bag at the Nov. 4 race, according to an e-mailed statement from
the New York Road Runners.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  